Embedding provider management and testing

Usage: do-memory-cli embedding <COMMAND>

Commands:
  test            Test embedding provider connectivity and configuration
  config          Show current embedding configuration
  list-providers  List available embedding providers
  benchmark       Benchmark embedding provider performance
  enable          Enable embeddings in the current session
  disable         Disable embeddings in the current session
  help            Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
